span.p:
FETCH Stage
1. Get instruction from text_map at PC
2. IR = instruction.machine_code
3. PC_temp = PC
4. PC += 4
5. Update stage to DECODE

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
DECODE Stage
Decode instruction based on format
Update control.MuxA and control.MuxB

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
EXECUTE Stage
Perform ALU operation based on instruction
Update control.ALU

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
MEMORY ACCESS Stage
Update MAR, MDR based on instruction
Update PC for branches/jumps

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
WRITEBACK Stage
1. Update RY based on MuxY
2. Write to register file
3. x0 always = 0
4. Mark instruction as FINISHED
